Date: 20011208
Short: germanpw40
Title: Deutscher (German) Perl-Workshop 4.0

<p>A call for participation has gone out for the 4th German Perl
Workshop. It will be held in Sankt Augustin, Germany (near to Bonn and
Cologne), from Feb 13 until 15, 2002. The call for participation is
available in German [http://www.perlworkshop.de/2002/cfp-4-de.htm] and
English [http://www.perlworkshop.de/2002/cfp-4-en.htm].  Please visit
the German Perl Workshop 2002 Web Site
[http://www.perlworkshop.de/2002/] for more details.</p>
